                     <interp inst="t18280110-33-person332" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I called at Miss Ward's about seven o'clock in the evening of the 28th of November, some young man answered the door; I cannot say whether it was the prisoner or not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-33-person333">
                  JOHN 
                  BEE
               <interp inst="t18280110-33-person333" type="surname" value="BEE"></interp>
